{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[D]  [E] Well, you [A]may be the king of this discotheque thing
But, honey,[Bm]  I ain't looking for that
What I need[D] is a man not some so called aristocrat
[A] Oh, if only you'd waited or just hesitated
Or [Bm]maybe just asked me to dance
But you [D]really don't know why I don't wanna go
And, baby, [A]that's why we don't stand[E] a chance
{end_of_verse}


